## Third-Party Attributions

This project uses data and APIs from the following third-party services:

### MangaDex

- Website: <https://mangadex.org>
- API: <https://api.mangadex.org>
- Terms of Service: <https://mangadex.org/terms>

All manga metadata, cover images, and chapter information are provided by MangaDex
and remain the property of their respective copyright holders.

### AniList

- Website: <https://anilist.co>
- API: <https://anilist.gitbook.io/anilist-apiv2-docs/>
- Terms of Service: <https://anilist.co/terms>

User data and manga information are accessed via the AniList API with user consent
through OAuth2 authentication.

### Claude Code (Anthropic)

- Website: <https://claude.ai>
- Developed by: Anthropic PBC

This project was developed with assistance from Claude, Anthropic's AI assistant.
Claude Code provided architectural guidance, code implementation assistance, and
best practices consultation throughout the development process.

